Cell["\<\
The expressions of the amplitudes associated to each left-dressed disjoint \
direct Feynman diagram are calculated in time representation.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8982551888079557`*^9, 3.898255239729643*^9}, {
